v→0 adiabatic limit: dp_+/dt = -Γ_+(t)p_+ + Γ_-(t)p_- with fast relaxation.
Quasi-static solution: p_+(t) = Γ_-(t)/(Γ_+(t)+Γ_-(t)) = 1/(1+e^{ħΩ(t)/k_B T}).
At t→∞: Ω(∞)=Δ/ħ → p_+(∞) = 1/(1+e^{ħΔ/k_B T}).
```

